  "total_duration": 488.251,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 17.24,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象一个亲戚在很远的地方住了很久，明年终于要回来。她以为家里还是记忆中的样子，可是等她回来，也许会看到一栋完全不同的新房子。这种 surprise，不是礼物盒那种惊喜，而是“家已经变了”的惊讶。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 17.59,
      "end": 36.141,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A new house"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“新居”。这课先要看懂距离："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Nigeria"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是非洲的一个国家，离"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "England"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很远。姐姐住在那里，所以她没有亲眼看到家里的房子一步步建好。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 36.491,
      "end": 49.083,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还要看懂一个容易误会的词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "country"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这课里不是“国家”，而是 countryside，乡下、乡间。叙述者一家现在住在乡下的一栋 beautiful new house 里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 49.433,
      "end": 71.865,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这栋房子很"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "modern"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是风格新、设计新，不等于一定更好；它看起来"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "strange"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也不是坏或丑，而是和周围传统的房子不太一样。故事的核心就是：远方的姐姐回来时，会发现家变成了一栋在老地区里很现代的新房子。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 72.214,
      "end": 90.798,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事从一封信开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I had a letter from my sister yesterday. She lives in Nigeria."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "姐姐在非洲的 Nigeria，离 England 很远。她写信不是说房子，而是说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "she would come to England next year"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，她明年会来英国。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 91.148,
      "end": 108.78,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接下来出现真正的 surprise："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "If she comes, she will get a surprise."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么？因为家已经变了。叙述者一家现在住在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a beautiful new house in the country"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里的 country 是 countryside，乡下，不是 nation 国家。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 109.13,
      "end": 128.469,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "时间线要听清楚："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Work on it had begun before my sister left."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "房子的工程在姐姐离开以前就已经开始了。后来"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The house was completed five months ago."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，五个月前房子建好了。姐姐没看到中间过程，所以回来才会惊讶。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 128.819,
      "end": 149.407,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个新家不是冷冰冰的建筑展示。叙述者已经告诉姐姐："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "she could stay with us"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，她可以住在我们家。房子有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "many large rooms"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a lovely garden"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。它非常 modern，所以有些人觉得 strange；它大概是整个 district 里唯一一栋现代房子。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 149.756,
      "end": 151.836,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你觉得姐姐为什么会 surprised？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 152.186,
      "end": 159.39,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为她住在 Nigeria，很远，没有看到房子慢慢建好。她回来时，家已经不一样了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 159.74,
      "end": 170.0,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。她记得的是离开前的家；她明年看到的，可能是一栋 completed new house。这就是 distance 加 time 带来的 surprise。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 170.35,
      "end": 175.295,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "modern"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是不是一定比 old house 更好？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 175.645,
      "end": 187.205,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。modern 只是说风格新、设计新、可能有大窗户和更简洁的外形。old house 可以很温暖，modern house 也可以很温暖。课文不是比赛谁更高级。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 187.555,
      "end": 192.296,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "strange"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "呢？是不是很难看？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 192.646,
      "end": 205.366,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也不是。strange 在这里是 unfamiliar，别人不熟悉、不习惯。想象一条老街上突然开了一座玻璃图书馆，可能很好用，但第一眼会显得 strange。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 205.716,
      "end": 208.821,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "district"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是什么意思？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 209.171,
      "end": 224.451,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "district 是一个地区、附近一带，可以理解成 local area 或 neighbourhood。课文最后说它 must be the only modern house in the district，就是这栋现代房子在周围旧式房子里特别显眼。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 224.801,
      "end": 231.352,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这课真正的结尾不是“我们家很豪华”，而是“它很现代，所以在老地区里看起来不同”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 231.701,
      "end": 238.901,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "完全对。新房子 strange，不是因为坏，而是因为它是 district 里唯一的 modern house。"
        }
      ]
    },
