        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "district"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是地区、附近一带。你可以把它想成 neighbourhood 或 local area。课文说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the only modern house in the district"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是这片地方里可能都是传统房子，只有这一栋特别现代。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 346.008,
      "end": 363.247,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 不从大表格开始，我们把它看成一条 house timeline。姐姐昨天写信，说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "she would come to England next year"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "would come"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是过去说的未来：她在信里说“明年会来”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 363.597,
      "end": 384.537,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后是可能发生的未来："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "If she comes, she will get a surprise."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果她来了，她就会惊讶。为什么？因为更早以前，房子的工程"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had begun before my sister left"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had begun"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "告诉你：工程开始这件事，比姐姐离开还早。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 384.887,
      "end": 408.566,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后，房子"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was completed five months ago"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这是 passive voice，被动语态，重点放在 the house was finished，而不是谁完成了它。所以这课的英语在帮我们排顺序：had begun，was completed，said she would come，If she comes, she will get a surprise。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 408.916,
      "end": 426.996,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的“离开一段时间、回来发现地方变了”放进你自己的生活。下面三个场景都要填，word bank 里选短语。你可以讲亲戚明年来家里，也可以讲开学回教室、回小区、去爷爷奶奶家，重点是时间、变化和 surprise。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 427.346,
      "end": 445.146,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
